comments: Garland (CLE) and Harris (ORL) engage and disengage with one another near the free throw line.
Carter Jr. (ORL) firms up in his screening position in Okoro's (CLE) path and absorbs the contact.
Anthony (ORL) goes to, not through, Garland's (CLE) space and marginal contact occurs to Garland's front during Anthony's natural shooting motion.
Garland (CLE) is jumping away from Anthony (ORL) and retreating toward the baseline when marginal contact occurs with Anthony's side during the driving shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) is late to the spot and does not establish a legal guarding position as Okoro (CLE) slips the contact after his gather.
Harris (ORL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes three steps before attempting the shot.

Garland (CLE) brushes Harris' (ORL) right arm after his gather and Harris is able to move through the marginal contact to continue on his path to the basket. Allen (CLE) jumps alongside Harris' path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Ennis III (ORL) legally contests Love's (CLE) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Allen (CLE) jumps vertically and absorbs the marginal body contact initiated by Anthony (ORL) during the driving shot attempt.
Anthony (ORL) is moving slightly forward when marginal body contact occurs with Garland (CLE) at the end of the drive.
Carter Jr. (ORL) could be deemed to be imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Garland (CLE) extends forward and delivers body contact to Anthony (ORL) along the sideline.
Allen (CLE) establishes himself in a screening position in Harris' (ORL) path and absorbs the contact.
Harris (ORL) and Garland (CLE) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Harris (ORL) is moving forward when marginal contact occurs with Love's (CLE) front as he receives the pass.
Anthony (ORL) legally contests Osman's (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Ennis III (ORL).
